According to the letter, Parli, Ambajogai, Kej, Dharur, Majalgaon, Vadwani, Beed, Patoda, and Beed districts of the state are covered.
A proposal to the government to upgrade the main district road in Shirurkasar taluka as a state highway.
has been presented.
Considering the number of villages on these roads, population, road usage and demand,
The government was considering upgrading these roads as state highways.
The Government's Decisions:
Proposal by Chief Engineer, Public Works Regional Department, Chhatrapati Sambhajinagar
Considering Parli, Ambajogai, Kej, Dharur, Majalgaon, Vadwani, Beed, Patoda and Beed districts.
The following major district roads in Shirurkasar taluka are being upgraded as state highways.
